Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the final safety lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, just concentrate on walking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It walked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, calm down! That's not your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with the\NEva's defense system?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The signal's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The field's not deploying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Left arm damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The circuits have disconnected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a crack on the front of the cranium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The armor won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The head's been damaged!\NExtent of damage, unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The control nerves are disconnecting\None after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not getting any readings on the pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know this ceiling.
