Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as it was fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A disaster comes as it will, without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We could say it was fortunate, in the sense\Nthat our prior investments were not a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be sure about that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't pay off, it's a waste all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely. Now that the Angels,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fact that we have been\Nmanipulating information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,have become public knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv must operate in a speedy\Nand prudent manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been taken care of.\NYou may rest assured of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.52,BG,,0,0,0,,In regards to the declaration of\Nthe special state of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.10,BG,,0,0,0,,government officials have announced...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.31,BG,,0,0,0,,This incident was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.52,BG,,0,0,0,,UN forces in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's public scenario B-22.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.86,BG,,0,0,0,,In response to reporters' questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.11,BG,,0,0,0,,No, there's no threat of contamination\Nfrom the center of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're hushing up the truth again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least our PR people are thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.86,BG,,0,0,0,,The only Angel samples collected\Nwere adhered to the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that they've finally got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being pretty casual about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:12.87,BG,,0,0,0,,Correct, as in the model simulation,\Napproximately 99.9% of it evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.\NI think everyone's actually scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we must acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Ikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't there a better way to\Nutilize Nerv and Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First the repairs to Unit 00,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and now to Unit 01, which you\Nwrecked in its first battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough to bankrupt an entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We also understand that you\Ngave that toy to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Manpower, time, and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more do you and your family\Nplan on wasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.40,BG,,0,0,0,,And that is not your only responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(945.6,285.4)}{\pos(316.8,131.8)}Top Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}{\pos(960,541.4)}Human Instrumentality Project
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(960,627.8)}{\pos(955.2,621.4)}United Nations Top Executive Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(960,755.8)}{\pos(960,754.2)}17th Midterm Report
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(958.4,799)}{\pos(960,851.8)}Human Instrumentality Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,919.2)}2015 Business Plan Outline Summary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.03,BG,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that should be your top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Under these desperate circumstances,\Nthat project is our one and only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we cannot excuse any delays\Nin that project's schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the reappearance of the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will consider the issue\Nregarding the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the rest of this meeting\Nconcerns only the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your presence here was appreciated, Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, there is no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind has no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Air conditioning has just got to be\Nmankind's greatest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the triumph of science over nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No external injuries. His memory\Nis a bit muddled, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think it could it be\Nmental contamination?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There appears to be no cause for worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose he did have a pretty hectic day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not suprising. His cranial nerves\Ntook a lot of strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Construction Plan Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Keep it coming. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If Eva and this city both operate\Nat their full potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we can make it through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to defeat the Angels?\NYou're always such an optimist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sometimes you need a little wishful\Nthinking just to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your point. It helps to\Nhear things like that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want to live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that living apart is natural\Nfor Ikari and his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And being together is unnatural?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.22,Signs,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. His room will be in the 6th Block,\Njust beyond this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that satisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'd rather be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I said, I'll take care of Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got permission from the brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not like I'm going to\N"put the moves" on a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course you're not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell are you thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're always like that. Honestly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're always like that. Honestly!{\i0}\NShe just can't take a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll have to have a party tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A welcoming party for my\Nnew roommate, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're going to move after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I never dreamed that this city\Nwould become a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband's saying that our kid and I\Nshould evacuate, at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This city may be a fortress, but that's\Nno guarantee of safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remembering yesterday\Ngives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind if we make\Na little stop on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Someplace really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just such a lonely city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! The buildings are growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is a fortress, designed to\Nprotect against the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is New Tokyo-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the city that you helped to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your things should have already\Nbeen delivered, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I just recently moved\Nto this city too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, this is YOUR home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the place\Nis a little bit messy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You call this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a "little bit" messy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry! Could you put the food\Nin the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,snacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and nothing but beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a life does she lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. What's in the other fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't mind that.\NHe's probably still sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Life just doesn't get any better than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to eat?\NIt's pretty good, even if it is instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm just not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no excuse! You can't be so finicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Having dinner with somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon! Pon! Pon! Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:06.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,139.2)}Our Chores Chart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:06.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(942.396,310.4)}Day/Chore     Su      M      T     W      Th        F       S
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:06.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(951.98,468.8)}Breakfast     S        S       M       S      S        S       S
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:06.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(975.993,654.4)}Dinner         S        S       S      M      S        S       M
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That should be it for fairly\Nsplitting up the chores!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, this is your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can take advantage\Nof everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. All you keep saying is yes, yes, yes.\NIt's so depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a boy, aren't you?\NAct like a man! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go take a bath and\Nscrub away all those bad memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathing is the laundry of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A p... p... p...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him? He's one of those new\Nhot spring penguins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Pen Pen.\NHe's your other roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cover that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:17.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1204.9,848.7)}{\pos(1401.7,763.9)}Toothpicks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I've been a little bit TOO cheery?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm the one who's transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathing is the laundry of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But bad memories always seem to find me\Nwhen I'm in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My father
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rei Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how was Rei today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the hospital this\Nafternoon, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be ready to work again in twenty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By then, we'll be ready to re-activate\NUnit 00 from cryo-stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be so hard on those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one else who can pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they survive, that is what\NI'll have them do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With no regard to what they may want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,Little Shin's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.17,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1156.8,247)}{\frz334.4\pos(1108.8,224.6)}No. 1 Public Middle School Transfer Application\NShinji Ikari
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after all the horrible stuff\Nhe went through,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no telling if he'll pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintaining him is part of your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just scared. I don't know\Nhow to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Grumbling already? You were the one\Nwho had the bright idea of taking him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, I was thinking of Shinji as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as bad as Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We destroyed that Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I can't be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Another ceiling I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. In this whole city,\Nthere's no place that's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The head has been damaged!\NExtent of damage, unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having problems\Nmaintaining activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The synchrograph is reversing!\NThe pulses are flowing backward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the circuit! Block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rejecting the signal! It won't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His monitors aren't responding.\NLife signs unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 's gone completely silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort the operation!\NRescuing the pilot is our first priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Force eject the entry plug!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't! It's completely out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva's re-activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! There's no way it can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone berserk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An AT field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No! As long as the Angel\Nhas that AT field up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't touch the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Left arm, regenerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has deployed its AT field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's neutralizing the phase space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's eroding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It went through that AT field so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to self-destruct?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the Eva's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Circuits reconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Systems restored. Graphs back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot life signs, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out the recovery team. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Preserving the pilot's life is our first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a very praiseworthy thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.46,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(1032.2,683.8)}{\pos(1003.4,671)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.86,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840.2,23)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As Shinji lives his new life,\Ndrifting along without direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no way for him to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that he is an Eva pilot\Nmakes him popular in his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Evangelion: "The Silent Phone"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you fan service next time too!
